projects.name: Ebill management system
projects.description: This application provides a platform, where customers can pay their bills with a credit card, debit card, or transfer funds directly from bank accounts using electronic funds transfer (EFT). While customers set up their accounts, they can choose whether they want automatic bill payment, for a set and forget experience. Payments can be automatically deducted from the payment method based on the chosen frequency. Also provided bill display to check monthly billing details for end-users. As per PCI standards all the transactions are handled on secure servers and all sensitive data is encrypted. Implemented notification modules which handles all notifications related to the payment status.
projects.skills: WordPress, HTML5, CSS3, jQuery, JavaScript, MySQL, Jira

projects.name: Tourism Project
projects.description: Developed tourism projects using React and Redux delivering high performance features. Technologies used included Node.js RESTful API development and webservices. Worked on the front-end architecture developed in React. I was responsible for the on-production page's performance and optimization.
projects.skills: Node.js, React, Redux, RESTful API, HTML, CSS

projects.name: Fleet Management System
projects.description: The vehicle management system is a python-based project. We have developed a vehicle management system using Python Fastapi, Angular, Mongodb. The main modules developed in this project are, oil module, Vehicle Management, Vehicle Info and the Driver module along with a booking engine. Created the admin panel to create building data using angular and fastapi. Building data is stored in Postgresdb. And user details are stored in the mongodB. Wrote test cases and executed using automation.
projects.skills: Python, Fast API, Angular, MongoDB, Postgres, Azure Cloud
